    <item>
      <title>韩元跌至三个月低点后，韩国誓言应对波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/korea-vows-to-fight-volatility-after-won-hits-three-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国财政部长承诺将迅速采取行动，抑制韩元过度波动，这是韩元跌至三个月低点后官员们对韩元日益感到紧张的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/korea-vows-to-fight-volatility-after-won-hits-three-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>养老金改革遭否决，乌拉圭大选进入决选阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uruguay-presidential-candidates-orsi-delgado-headed-to-runoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于两位候选人均未获得获胜所需的绝对多数票，且该国养老金制度的一项备受争议的改革法案未能通过，乌拉圭总统选举将于下个月进入决选阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uruguay-presidential-candidates-orsi-delgado-headed-to-runoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:42:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因日本大选结果和油价暴跌而走弱：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本执政联盟未能赢得议会多数席位后，日元下跌，引发人们猜测政治不确定性将使央行的鹰派立场减弱。以色列避开伊朗石油设施袭击后，原油价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列限制伊朗袭击军事目标 油价暴跌 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/brent-falls-5-at-open-after-israel-strikes-avoid-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周初，以色列对伊朗目标的袭击避开了伊朗的原油设施，这增加了该地区敌对状态缓和的可能性，导致油价下跌逾 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/brent-falls-5-at-open-after-israel-strikes-avoid-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:03:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
